enb_long_title: Twentieth Session of the Subsidiary Bodies to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: This event took place on Monday, 21 June, and was chaired by Murray Ward (New Zealand).
The event included presentations on modeling and assessment of contributions to climate change (MATCH), and on policy options under the Brazilian Proposal.
A summary of these discussions is available at: http://www.iisd.ca/vol12/enb12238e.html.
